{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6ecb0bd9d880b1d8a406f850265\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_3b6badec02d2ad20b444c40e08224e2d\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"月圆之夜CCG开发群\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_3b6badec02d2ad20b444c40e08224e2d\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-06-03 17:30 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"月圆之夜CCG开发群\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"history_count\": 5\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_3b6badec02d2ad20b444c40e08224e2d\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_3b6badec02d2ad20b444c40e08224e2d\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_3b6badec02d2ad20b444c40e08224e2d\"\n}\n```\n\nChat history since last reply (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"ou_3b6badec02d2ad20b444c40e08224e2d\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1780468191056,\n    \"body\": \"ou_3b6badec02d2ad20b444c40e08224e2d: <media:image>\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"ou_3b6badec02d2ad20b444c40e08224e2d\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1780468191372,\n    \"body\": \"ou_3b6badec02d2ad20b444c40e08224e2d: <media:image>\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"ou_3b6badec02d2ad20b444c40e08224e2d\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1780468191700,\n    \"body\": \"ou_3b6badec02d2ad20b444c40e08224e2d: <media:image>\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"ou_3b6badec02d2ad20b444c40e08224e2d\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1780468192001,\n    \"body\": \"ou_3b6badec02d2ad20b444c40e08224e2d: <media:image>\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"ou_348eeddd81d4c03865f9f1684fce6966\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1780477052074,\n    \"body\": \"兵王(周以天): [【V2.0周版本】2026.06.04 周版本 - 飞书云文档](https://ztgame.feishu.cn/wiki/MrHjwTrEhiVC9NknvbIc4X6YnMf)<at user_id=\\\"ou_3b6badec02d2ad20b444c40e08224e2d\\\">吴凯彬</at> <at user_id=\\\"ou_e0151fb79bfe816bb40c8754c709d046\\\">敖亚军</at> 看看还有什么缺少的功能\"\n  }\n]\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-ru